            <text>
                <body>
                    <div type="edition">
                        <div type="textpart">
                            <ab><persName><name ref="Berno">Berno</name></persName> filius
                                <persName><name ref="Berno">Berni</name></persName>
                        <persName><name ref="Iohannes">Iohanni</name></persName> (…) pro redemptione
                        dona in <rs key="#Churches">ecclesia</rs> que est <rs key="#Monasteries"
                            >monasterium</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Churches #Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/126">Sancti
                            Bartholomei</orgName> apostoli qui ponitur in <placeName
                            key="#Monasteries" ref="#places/281">Sestinge Curte
                            Maymbertii</placeName> de omnibus rebus meis <rs key="#Demesnes"
                            >donnicatis</rs> et <rs key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie"
                            >massaritiis</rs> quanticunque habere (…) visum sum infra <rs
                            key="#Comitatus">comitatu et territorio</rs>
                        <geogName key="#Comitatus" ref="#estates/154">Rosellensi</geogName> in loco
                        ubi dicitur <placeName key="#Demesnes #Casae/cassinae_massaricie">Valle
                            Petrosula</placeName> sive per aliis locis (…) ubicumque de mea
                        hereditate inventa fuerit, con le pertinenze, sicut michi evenit per
                        successionem de quondam genitore meo et genitrice mea. Pena del doppio.
                        Chiede a <persName key="#Writer #Notary #Judge"><name ref="Romanus"
                                >Romanum</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarium</rs> et <rs key="#Judge">iudicem</rs> donni
                        imperatoris la stesura della cartula. Actum <placeName ref="#places/281"
                            >Sestinge</placeName>. Testimoni: <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Pepo">Pepi</name></persName> filii <persName><name ref="Berno"
                                >Berni</name></persName>
                        <persName><name ref="Raccorus">Raccori</name></persName>; <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Rustichellus">Rustichelli</name></persName>
                        germano suo; <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Corbulus"
                            >Corbuli</name></persName> filii <persName><name ref="Berno"
                                >Berni</name></persName>
                        <persName><name ref="Martinus">Martini</name></persName>. Scrive: Romanus
                        notarius et iudex donni imperatoris.</ab>
                        </div>
                    </div>
